@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Root View Weight App Header'
define root  view entity ZWBI_I_WEIGHT_HEAD
 as select from zwbi_vinh as _Head
composition [0..*] of ZWBI_I_WEIGHT_ITEM as _Item
{
  key inward_uuid as InwardUuid,
      ticknum     as Ticknum,
      fiscal      as Fiscal,
      intype      as Intype,
      indate      as Indate,
      intime      as Intime,
      vehnum      as Vehnum,
      drivname    as Drivname,
      drivnum     as Drivnum,
      tranname    as Tranname,
      orderhead   as Orderhead,  
      plant       as Plant,
      planttext   as Planttext,
      type        as Type,
      dchannel    as Dchannel,
      range       as Range,
      itemunit    as Itemunit,
      grossweight as Grossweight,
      netweight   as Netweight,
      printform   as printform,
      pwidate     as pwidate,
      pwiempwg    as pwiempwg,
      pwigetwg    as pwigetwg,
      pwitime     as pwitime,
      pwiuom      as pwiuom,
      pwodate     as pwodate,
      pwoempwg    as pwoempwg,
      pwogetwg    as pwogetwg,
      pwotime     as pwotime,
      pwexit      as pwexit,
      pwexitdt    as pwexitdt,
      pwexittm    as pwexittm,
      pwoempwg_f  as Pwoempwg_f,           
      pwiempwg_f  as Pwiempwg_f,          
      gunit_f     as Gunit_f,                  
      tunit_f     as Tunit_f, 
      itemunit_f  as Itemunit_f,      //25/10/2024       
      created_by            as CreatedBy,
      created_on            as CreatedOn,
      created_tm            as CreatedTm,
      created_at            as CreatedAt,
      last_changed_by       as LastChangedBy,
      last_changed_on       as LastChangedOn,
      local_last_changed_at as LocalLastChangedAt,      
     _Item // Make association public
}
